<title>Colin Powell&#39;s lies</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://theintercept.com/2018/02/06/lie-after-lie-what-colin-powell-knew-about-iraq-fifteen-years-ago-and-what-he-told-the-un/&#34;&gt;A detailed breakdown&lt;/a&gt; of the lies that Colin Powell told the UN and the public to give &lt;a href=&#34;/glossary.html#dubya&#34;&gt;Dubya&lt;/a&gt; an excuse to invade Iraq. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Powell, and &lt;a href=&#34;/glossary.html#dubya&#34;&gt;Dubya&lt;/a&gt;, must bear some of the guilt for the subsequent suffering in Iraq, including the existence of &lt;a href=&#34;/glossary.html#pissi&#34;&gt;PISSI&lt;/a&gt;.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
